OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,5,
OL,6,FStill it could insist on a separate
OL,7,Fnews service for the former Grampian
OL,8,Fregion remaining. Stranger things have
OL,9,Fhappened.
OL,11,FThis clearly would mean keeping a large
OL,12,Feditorial operation in Aberdeen and the
OL,13,Fnorth of Scotland.
OL,15,FStudio presentation and production can
OL,16,Fmove to Glasgow without Ofcom
OL,17,Fpermission.
