OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,5,
OL,6,FRealistically, if any dedicated output
OL,7,Ffor the north remained it would have to
OL,8,Fbe recorded.
OL,10,FMy own suspicion is that Ofcom will
OL,11,Feither approve STV's proposals -
OL,12,Fdespite huge political objections - or
OL,13,Finsist on a sub-opt for the north. Even
OL,14,Fdoing this could still save jobs.
OL,16,FIt is important to remember that STV's
OL,17,Fcurrent service includes both Scottish
OL,18,Fnational news and stories of local and
OL,19,Fregional interest.
