OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,5,
OL,6,FAll the news programmes in the nations
OL,7,Fare very different editorially to
OL,8,FEnglish regional programmes.
OL,10,FSTV currently has one advantage over
OL,11,Fthe BBC - it can also cover the kind of
OL,12,Flocal and regional stories which are
OL,13,Funlikely to be seen on Reporting
OL,14,FScotland.
OL,16,FBut is it fair to impose an obligation
OL,17,Fon a commercial broadcaster to do
OL,18,Fsomething which the BBC has never done?
OL,20,FThis is not 1961 or even 1993.
OL,23,Uppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
