OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,5,
OL,6,FOr does the simple fact that ratings
OL,7,Ffor STV North are good mean that taking
OL,8,Fthe axe to the service is a huge
OL,9,Fmisjudgement?
OL,11,FSTV points out that it's legal
OL,12,Fobligations are greater than those of
OL,13,FUTV and ITV Wales.
OL,15,FAgainst this are two obvious points.
OL,16,FScotland is bigger than Wales or
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland and has always been
OL,18,Fsplit into three channel 3 regions.
