OL,3,GOPINIONCSTV starts search for redundancies but
OL,4,COfcom decision could be months away
OL,5,
OL,6,FAdd on changing consumer behaviour and
OL,7,Fyou can see that there is at least an
OL,8,Fargument - if not necessarily a
OL,9,Fcompelling case - for change.
OL,11,FThe actual boundary between STV's two
OL,12,Fregions merely reflects transmitter
OL,13,Fareas. It is not as simple as saying
OL,14,FAberdeen is different to Glasgow.
OL,16,FIt is for all those reasons that Ofcom
OL,17,Fmay face big questions if it does not
OL,18,Frun a lengthy, detailed consultation.
