OL,5,
OL,6,FUnions and politicians will be critical
OL,7,Fif Ofcom simply puts a proposed change
OL,8,Fof this magnitude out to a short
OL,9,Fconsultation.
OL,11,FMeanwhile you can expect the unions to
OL,12,Fstep up their fight if compulsory
OL,13,Fredundancies look likely.
OL,15,FThis story could prove very significant
OL,16,Fover the coming months.
